    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1875-01-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1875-01-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="113"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d113">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Sutter</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Foster</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Acapulco</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-01-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">January</hi> 28.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">[Received in Mexico 28th, 7 p.m.]</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Minister of the United States</hi>:</p>
                <p>Indians and coast-guard threaten Acapulco if the <hi rend="italic">cura</hi> is
                    arrested. The federal garrison insufficient to sustain the judge of the
                    district. National guards under arms. The governor <hi rend="italic">en
                        route</hi> for Acapulco.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>J. A. SUTTER.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
